<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Mr. Benji's Book Creator · #readabook</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka+One&family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #fef9f0;
  --ink: #1e1410;
  --card: #ffffff;
  --muted: #8a7a6a;
  --radius: 16px;
  --shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);

  /* tone colors - set dynamically */
  --tone-bg: #fff0f0;
  --tone-accent: #e63946;
  --tone-dark: #9b1b26;
}

* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

body {
  font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--ink);
  min-height: 100vh;
  padding-bottom: 3rem;
}

/* ── HEADER ── */
header {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 2rem 1rem 1.5rem;
  background: white;
  border-bottom: 3px solid #f0e8d8;
}

.header-lion { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }

header h1 {
  font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
  font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.6rem);
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: 1;
}

header h1 em {
  color: #e63946;
  font-style: normal;
}

.header-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 0.4rem;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  color: var(--muted);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* ── SCREENS ── */
.screen { display: none; }
.screen.active { display: block; }

/* ── FORM ── */
.form-wrap {
  max-width: 620px;
  margin: 2rem auto;
  padding: 0 1rem;
}

.step-card {
  background: var(--card);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  border: 2px solid #f0e8d8;
}

.step-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.step-question {
  font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

/* Text inputs */
.text-input {
  width: 100%;
  border: 2px solid #e8dfd0;
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 0.65rem 1rem;
  font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--ink);
  background: #fef9f0;
  outline: none;
  transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
}
.text-input:focus {
  border-color: #e63946;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(230,57,70,0.12);
}
.text-input::placeholder { color: #c4b8a8; font-weight: 400; }

/* Emoji genre picker */
.emoji-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.emoji-btn {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
  padding: 0.7rem 0.4rem;
  border: 2.5px solid #e8dfd0;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: #fef9f0;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
}

.emoji-btn:hover { border-color: #c4b8a8; background: #fff; transform: translateY(-2px); }

.emoji-btn.selected {
  border-color: #e63946;
  background: #fff0f1;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(230,57,70,0.2);
}

.emoji-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; line-height: 1; }
.emoji-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--muted); text-align: center; }
.emoji-btn.selected .emoji-label { color: #e63946; }

/* Color tone picker */
.color-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.color-btn {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 1rem 0.5rem 0.7rem;
  border: 2.5px solid #e8dfd0;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: white;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
}

.color-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); border-color: #c4b8a8; }

.color-btn.selected { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }

.color-swatch {
  width: 36px; height: 36px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

.color-word {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 800;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.color-vibe { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600; }

/* Scale slider */
.scale-wrap { padding: 0.5rem 0; }

.scale-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}

.scale-slider {
  flex: 1;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, #a8d8a8, #ffcc5c, #ff6b6b);
  outline: none;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.scale-slider::-webkit-slider-thumb {
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  width: 26px; height: 26px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: white;
  border: 3px solid #e63946;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  cursor: grab;
  transition: transform 0.1s;
}
.scale-slider::-webkit-slider-thumb:active { cursor: grabbing; transform: scale(1.15); }

.scale-value {
  font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  color: #e63946;
  min-width: 24px;
  text-align: center;
}

.scale-labels {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--muted);
  padding: 0 2px;
}

/* ── CREATE BUTTON ── */
.btn-create {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 1rem;
  background: #e63946;
  color: white;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 14px;
  font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 0 #9b1b26, 0 6px 16px rgba(230,57,70,0.3);
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}
.btn-create:hover { background: #c1121f; transform: translateY(-1px); }
.btn-create:active { transform: translateY(2px); box-shadow: 0 2px 0 #9b1b26; }

.error-msg {
  background: #fff0f1;
  border: 2px solid #ffa5ab;
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
  color: #c1121f;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-top: 0.8rem;
  display: none;
}

/* ── BOOK SCREEN ── */
#book-screen { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 1.5rem 1rem 3rem; }

.book-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.book-cover-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
  border-radius: 99px;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  background: var(--tone-bg);
  color: var(--tone-dark);
}

.book-title-display {
  font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
  font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 5vw, 2.2rem);
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
}

.book-author-display {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-weight: 600;
}
.book-author-display span { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 800; }

/* Page card */
.page-card {
  background: white;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 2rem;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  border: 2px solid #f0e8d8;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  animation: fadeUp 0.3s ease-out;
  border-top: 5px solid var(--tone-accent);
  min-height: 280px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

.page-meta {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.chapter-tag {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--tone-accent);
}

.page-num {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.chapter-title {
  font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.chapter-body {
  font-family: 'Lora', serif;
  font-size: 14.5px;
  line-height: 1.85;
  color: #2a1f14;
  flex: 1;
}

.chapter-body p + p { margin-top: 0.8em; }

.drop-cap::first-letter {
  font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
  font-size: 3em;
  float: left;
  line-height: 0.78;
  margin: 0.05em 0.08em 0 0;
  color: var(--tone-accent);
}

.chapter-footer {
  margin-top: 1rem;
  padding-top: 0.8rem;
  border-top: 1px solid #f0e8d8;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #c4b8a8;
}

/* Nav */
.book-nav {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  padding: 0.5rem 0;
}

.nav-btn {
  width: 48px; height: 48px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid #e8dfd0;
  background: white;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}
.nav-btn:hover:not(:disabled) { border-color: var(--tone-accent); color: var(--tone-accent); transform: scale(1.05); }
.nav-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.3; cursor: not-allowed; }

.nav-dots {
  display: flex;
  gap: 5px;
  align-items: center;
}

.nav-dot {
  width: 7px; height: 7px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: #e8dfd0;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.nav-dot.active { background: var(--tone-accent); width: 20px; border-radius: 4px; }

.book-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: 1.2rem;
}

.btn-action {
  padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 2px solid #e8dfd0;
  background: white;
  font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--muted);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.15s;
}
.btn-action:hover { border-color: var(--tone-accent); color: var(--tone-accent); }

/* Placeholder page */
.placeholder-banner {
  background: #fff9e6;
  border: 2px dashed #f0d080;
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 1rem;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #b08a00;
  margin-top: 1rem;
}

/* Progress bar */
.progress-bar-wrap {
  height: 4px;
  background: #f0e8d8;
  border-radius: 2px;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.progress-bar-fill {
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--tone-accent);
  border-radius: 2px;
  transition: width 0.3s;
}

@media print {
  header, .book-nav, .book-actions, .progress-bar-wrap { display: none !important; }
  .page-card { break-after: page; border: 1px solid #ddd; box-shadow: none; }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .emoji-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 0.4rem; }
  .emoji-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; }
  .color-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 0.4rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="app">

<header>
  <div class="header-lion">🦁</div>
  <h1>Mr. Benji's <em>Book Creator</em></h1>
  <span class="header-tag">#readabook</span>
</header>

<!-- ══ FORM SCREEN ══ -->
<div id="form-screen" class="screen active">
<div class="form-wrap">

  <!-- Student name -->
  <div class="step-card">
    <p class="step-label">Step 1</p>
    <p class="step-question">What's your name, author? ✍️</p>
    <input class="text-input" id="student-name" type="text" placeholder="Your first name" maxlength="30">
  </div>

  <!-- Book title -->
  <div class="step-card">
    <p class="step-label">Step 2</p>
    <p class="step-question">Give your book a cool title 📖</p>
    <input class="text-input" id="book-title" type="text" placeholder="e.g. The Last Signal" maxlength="50">
  </div>

  <!-- Main character -->
  <div class="step-card">
    <p class="step-label">Step 3</p>
    <p class="step-question">What's your main character's name? 🦸</p>
    <input class="text-input" id="char-name" type="text" placeholder="e.g. Zara, Marcus, Leo..." maxlength="30">
  </div>

  <!-- Setting -->
  <div class="step-card">
    <p class="step-label">Step 4</p>
    <p class="step-question">Where does your story happen? 🌍</p>
    <input class="text-input" id="setting" type="text" placeholder="e.g. a floating city, a jungle school..." maxlength="60">
  </div>

  <!-- Genre (emoji) -->
  <div class="step-card">
    <p class="step-label">Step 5</p>
    <p class="step-question">Pick a story world 👇</p>
    <div class="emoji-grid">
      <button class="emoji-btn" data-genre="sci-fi" onclick="pickGenre(this)">
        <span class="emoji-icon">🚀</span>
        <span class="emoji-label">Sci-Fi</span>
      </button>
      <button class="emoji-btn" data-genre="fantasy" onclick="pickGenre(this)">
        <span class="emoji-icon">🔮</span>
        <span class="emoji-label">Fantasy</span>
      </button>
      <button class="emoji-btn" data-genre="mystery" onclick="pickGenre(this)">
        <span class="emoji-icon">🔍</span>
        <span class="emoji-label">Mystery</span>
      </button>
      <button class="emoji-btn" data-genre="adventure" onclick="pickGenre(this)">
        <span class="emoji-icon">🌊</span>
        <span class="emoji-label">Adventure</span>
      </button>
      <button class="emoji-btn" data-genre="spooky" onclick="pickGenre(this)">
        <span class="emoji-icon">👻</span>
        <span class="emoji-label">Spooky</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tone (color) -->
  <div class="step-card">
    <p class="step-label">Step 6</p>
    <p class="step-question">Pick a color that matches your story's vibe 🎨</p>
    <div class="color-grid">
      <button class="color-btn" data-tone="intense" onclick="pickTone(this)" style="border-color:#e8dfd0;">
        <div class="color-swatch" style="background:#e63946;"></div>
        <span class="color-word" style="color:#e63946;">Red</span>
        <span class="color-vibe">Intense</span>
      </button>
      <button class="color-btn" data-tone="calm" onclick="pickTone(this)" style="border-color:#e8dfd0;">
        <div class="color-swatch" style="background:#457b9d;"></div>
        <span class="color-word" style="color:#457b9d;">Blue</span>
        <span class="color-vibe">Calm</span>
      </button>
      <button class="color-btn" data-tone="funny" onclick="pickTone(this)" style="border-color:#e8dfd0;">
        <div class="color-swatch" style="background:#f4a261;"></div>
        <span class="color-word" style="color:#d4690a;">Yellow</span>
        <span class="color-vibe">Funny</span>
      </button>
      <button class="color-btn" data-tone="mysterious" onclick="pickTone(this)" style="border-color:#e8dfd0;">
        <div class="color-swatch" style="background:#7b2d8b;"></div>
        <span class="color-word" style="color:#7b2d8b;">Purple</span>
        <span class="color-vibe">Mysterious</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Conflict scale -->
  <div class="step-card">
    <p class="step-label">Step 7</p>
    <p class="step-question">How much trouble does your character get into? ⚡</p>
    <div class="scale-wrap">
      <div class="scale-row">
        <input class="scale-slider" type="range" id="conflict-scale" min="1" max="5" value="3"
          oninput="updateScale(this.value)">
        <span class="scale-value" id="scale-display">3</span>
      </div>
      <div class="scale-labels">
        <span>😌 A little</span>
        <span>😅 Some</span>
        <span>😤 A lot</span>
        <span>😱 SO much</span>
        <span>🔥 EPIC</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="error-msg" id="error-msg"></div>
  <button class="btn-create" onclick="buildBook()">✨ Make My Book!</button>

</div>
</div>

<!-- ══ BOOK SCREEN ══ -->
<div id="book-screen" class="screen">
  <div class="book-header">
    <div class="book-cover-badge" id="book-badge">🚀 Sci-Fi · Intense</div>
    <h2 class="book-title-display" id="book-title-display"></h2>
    <p class="book-author-display">by <span id="book-author-display"></span></p>
  </div>

  <div class="progress-bar-wrap">
    <div class="progress-bar-fill" id="progress-fill" style="width:12.5%"></div>
  </div>

  <div id="page-container"></div>

  <div class="book-nav">
    <button class="nav-btn" id="prev-btn" onclick="navigate(-1)" disabled>‹</button>
    <div class="nav-dots" id="nav-dots"></div>
    <button class="nav-btn" id="next-btn" onclick="navigate(1)">›</button>
  </div>

  <div class="book-actions">
    <button class="btn-action" onclick="showScreen('form-screen')">← Start over</button>
    <button class="btn-action" onclick="window.print()">🖨 Print</button>
  </div>
</div>

</div><!-- end app -->

<script>
// ── STATE ──
let selectedGenre = null;
let selectedTone = null;
let currentPage = 0;
let pages = [];

// ── TONE COLORS ──
const toneConfig = {
  intense:    { accent: '#e63946', bg: '#fff0f1', dark: '#9b1b26', label: 'Intense 🔥' },
  calm:       { accent: '#457b9d', bg: '#eef4f8', dark: '#2a5068', label: 'Calm 🌊' },
  funny:      { accent: '#f4a261', bg: '#fff6ee', dark: '#9a4e0a', label: 'Funny 😂' },
  mysterious: { accent: '#7b2d8b', bg: '#f5eef8', dark: '#4a1757', label: 'Mysterious 🔮' },
};

const genreEmoji = {
  'sci-fi': '🚀', fantasy: '🔮', mystery: '🔍', adventure: '🌊', spooky: '👻'
};
const genreLabel = {
  'sci-fi': 'Sci-Fi', fantasy: 'Fantasy', mystery: 'Mystery', adventure: 'Adventure', spooky: 'Spooky'
};

// ── INPUT HANDLERS ──
function pickGenre(btn) {
  document.querySelectorAll('.emoji-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('selected'));
  btn.classList.add('selected');
  selectedGenre = btn.dataset.genre;
}

function pickTone(btn) {
  document.querySelectorAll('.color-btn').forEach(b => {
    b.classList.remove('selected');
    b.style.borderColor = '#e8dfd0';
  });
  btn.classList.add('selected');
  selectedTone = btn.dataset.tone;
  const cfg = toneConfig[selectedTone];
  btn.style.borderColor = cfg.accent;
}

function updateScale(val) {
  document.getElementById('scale-display').textContent = val;
}

// ── STORY DATABASE ──
// Slot key: genre-tone  (e.g. "sci-fi-intense")
// {char}, {setting}, {title} are replaced at render time

const STORIES = {

  /* ══ WRITTEN: 1 of 5 ══ Sci-Fi + Intense */
  'sci-fi-intense': [
    {
      title: "The Signal",
      text: `The day {char} discovered the signal, everything changed. It came through the old radio receiver in the corner of the lab — three short bursts, two long, then silence. Nobody else in {setting} had heard anything like it. {char} pressed the headphones tighter and held their breath.\n\nThe signal wasn't from Earth. The waveform on the screen proved it — no known satellite, no military frequency, nothing in any database. {char}'s hands were shaking as they began to record. Outside, the city hummed along as usual, unaware that one of its youngest residents had just made contact with something beyond the stars.\n\nThere was no one to call. No teacher would believe it. No parent would understand. So {char} did the only logical thing — they wrote back.`
    },
    {
      title: "Don't Tell Anyone",
      text: `The reply came in fourteen minutes. Fourteen minutes — not years, not decades like scientists always said it would take. Whatever was on the other end of that signal was close. Way too close.\n\nThe message decoded into a single sentence: WE HAVE BEEN WAITING FOR YOU, {char}.\n\nThey knew the name. {char} pushed back from the desk so hard the chair rolled into the wall. How? The receiver was offline, untraceable, just a hobby project built from junk parts. Nothing about it should have been traceable. And yet there it was, their name, glowing on the screen in green text like something out of a nightmare.\n\nOr maybe — just maybe — out of a dream.`
    },
    {
      title: "First Contact",
      text: `{char} typed back slowly: HOW DO YOU KNOW MY NAME?\n\nThe answer took thirty seconds this time. WE HAVE WATCHED {setting} FOR MANY YEARS. YOU ARE THE FIRST TO LISTEN.\n\nThat hit different. Not the first human — the first to listen. Which meant others had the equipment, others had the signal, and every single one of them had ignored it. {char} felt a strange mix of pride and terror settle in their stomach like a stone.\n\nWE NEED YOUR HELP, the screen flashed. THE ONES WHO HURT US ARE COMING. AND THEY KNOW WHERE YOU ARE TOO.\n\n{char} looked out the window at the familiar streets of {setting}. Nothing looked different. But everything had changed.`
    },
    {
      title: "The Hunters",
